verses.verse: A <S%H7892>Song<s%> of <S%H4609>degrees.<s%> To you <S%H5375>lift<s%> I up my <S%H5869>eyes,<s%> O you that <S%H3427>dwell<s%> in the <S%H8064>heavens.<s%>

<S%H2009>Behold,<s%> as the <S%H5869>eyes<s%> of <S%H5650>servants<s%> look to the <S%H3027>hand<s%> of their <S%H113>masters,<s%> and as the <S%H5869>eyes<s%> of a <S%H8198>maiden<s%> to the <S%H3027>hand<s%> of her <S%H1404>mistress;<s%> <S%H3651>so<s%> our <S%H5869>eyes<s%> wait on the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> our <S%H430>God,<s%> <S%H5704>until<s%> that he have <S%H2603>mercy<s%> on us.
Have <S%H2603>mercy<s%> on us, O <S%H3068>LORD,<s%> have <S%H2603>mercy<s%> on us: for we are <S%H7227>exceedingly<s%> <S%H7646>filled<s%> with <S%H937>contempt.<s%>

Our <S%H5315>soul<s%> is <S%H7227>exceedingly<s%> <S%H7646>filled<s%> with the <S%H3933>scorning<s%> of those that are at <S%H7600>ease,<s%> and with the <S%H937>contempt<s%> of the <S%H1349>proud.<s%>
